# 💡 LC3 Code Snippets - Copy/Paste Ready

## 🔁 Loop Templates

### Basic Counter Loop
```assembly
AND R1, R1, #0      ; counter = 0
LD R2, MAX          ; load limit
LOOP
    ; Your code here
    ADD R1, R1, #1  ; increment
    NOT R3, R2
    ADD R3, R3, #1  ; R3 = -MAX
    ADD R3, R1, R3  ; compare
    BRn LOOP        ; continue if < MAX
